</a> instead of this book.<br/>If you&apos;re never read any of the Darkover series, you might want to read<br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/472778.The_Heritage_of_Hastur__Darkover_Series_' title='The Heritage of Hastur (Darkover Series) by Marion Zimmer Bradley' rel='nofollow noopener'>
