</a> instead of this book.<br/>If you loved The Heritage of Hastur and<br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/567197.Sharra_s_Exile__Darkover_Series_' title='Sharra&apos;s Exile (Darkover Series) by Marion Zimmer Bradley' rel='nofollow noopener'>
