  <img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/books/1175044337s/472778.jpg" alt="The Heritage of Hastur (Darkover Series) by Marion Zimmer Bradley" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a> instead of this book.<br>If you loved The Heritage of Hastur and<br><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/567197.Sharra_s_Exile__Darkover_Series_" title="Sharra's Exile (Darkover Series) by Marion Zimmer Bradley" rel="nofollow noopener">
