<span id="freeTextContainer8362493098021644177">i fell in love with mikail and marguerida when i read traitor&apos;s sun. this books tells of marguerida&apos;s arrival on darkover and subsequent efforts to adjust to its strange ways. tho i haven&apos;t read bradley in a long time, i don&apos;t remember her being so wordy. i do remember her skill with prose and character development tho, and i find myself compelled to finish her books despite the long, dry passages with little or no action.</span>
